reviewText: KING FLEX love all his work!

Great dvd.  Very informative and entertaining.  Tariq Nasheed is on point as always and delivers a very upstanding and professional message that can be implemented into the socio-economic disposition of our people.
Very insightful and the way that it ties in relationships with history is great.  People would be so better off if they had knowledge of self, quality DVD.
Relationships, Riches, and Races is a very good and deep D.V.D.! Tariq went into deep topics on life and history. This is a must buy and a very excellent Live D.V.D.! No Doubt!!!
It was great! A lot of info that was much needed. I will be making more purchases in the future.
Not visually entertaining, would have been just as effective as an audible (iTunes, Mp3...etc). Very positive, ineresting, and enlightning. Touched on various subjects and leaves you wanting more.
